headline: /C O R R E C T I O N -- Kellanova/
summary: Eggo® is bringing breakfast to another dimension with a brand-new waffle inspired by Netflix's Stranger Things. Just in time for the fifth and final season, the brand is launching Eggo® Stranger Things Strawberry Waffles, its first-ever strawberry red waffle with colors from natural sources. The limited-edition waffle is designed to turn breakfast upside down with the irresistible taste fans know and love, making Eggo the perfect pairing for watch parties.
